Edith Sharpe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edith_Sharpe 0 Edith Sharpe (14 September 1894 – 6 June 1984) was a British actress. Born Edith Mary Sharpe in Hackney, London. She married Alexander Francis Part in 1931 and had one child. Died in Harrow on the Hill, London aged 89. Edith_Sharpe ( 14_September_1894 – 6_June_1984 ) was a_British_actress .
